<DATE>port-catsablefw 04 Oct 2003 - Experimental ABLE firmware support on cats
Chris Gilbert has added experimental ABLE firmware support on cats, please
see his <a href="http://mail-index.NetBSD.org/port-cats/2003/10/04/0000.html">mail</a>
