<DATE>pkgsrc-freeze200310 04 Oct 2003 - pkgsrc freeze
Starting Monday, October 6th, 2003, the <a
href="../Documentation/pkgsrc/">NetBSD Packages Collection</a> will be frozen
in order to stabilize pkgsrc on the various supported platforms.  See <a
href="http://mail-index.NetBSD.org/tech-pkg/2003/10/04/0015.html">Alistair
Crooks' message</a> to the tech-pkg mailing list for details.

