Matthew Green <a
href="http://mail-index.NetBSD.org/current-users/2003/09/22/0001.html">announced</a>
that he has
switched the <a href="..//Ports/alpha/">alpha</a>, <a
href="../Ports/i386/">i386</a>, <a
href="../Ports/sparc/">sparc</a> and <a
href="../Ports/sparc64/">sparc64</a> Ports to use GCC 3.3.1 
