<DATE>dump-011015 15 Oct 2001 - Timestamp capability added for dump's messages
    Brett Lymn has committed changes to dump(8), in <a 
    href="../Releases/current.html">NetBSD-current</a>, that allows one
    to add timestamps to the informational messages it prints.
